      "target": {
        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "refactor(review): remove PR egg hatching",
        "body": "## Summary\n\nRemove the PR egg hatching feature from ClawSweeper.\n\nThis removes the hatch repository dispatch path, hatch command classification/dispatch, separate PR egg comment sync, generated PR egg image publishing, and the PR egg rendering/generation helpers. The normal PR status label flow remains intact.\n\n## Background\n\nThe feature originated in the PR egg chain:\n\n- https://github.com/openclaw/clawsweeper/pull/120\n- https://github.com/openclaw/clawsweeper/pull/121\n- https://github.com/openclaw/clawsweeper/pull/122\n- https://github.com/openclaw/clawsweeper/pull/134\n\nThis is a surgical removal rather than a raw revert because the original introduction also included unrelated security hardening that should stay.\n\n## Impact\n\nUsers can no longer trigger `@clawsweeper hatch`, and ClawSweeper will no longer generate or publish PR egg image assets or marker-backed PR egg comments. Review, re-review, label sync, repair, and publish paths continue without the egg-specific side channel.\n\n## Validation\n\n- `pnpm run build:all`\n- `pnpm run lint`\n- `pnpm run test:unit`\n- `pnpm run test:repair`\n- `git diff --check`\n- `rg -n \"prEgg|PrEgg|PR_EGG|pr_egg|pr-eggs|PR egg|pr egg|egg|hatch|Hatch|clawsweeper-pr-egg|clawsweeper_hatch|hatch_pr_egg\" test src dashboard scripts .github/workflows/sweep.yml` returned no matches\n\n`pnpm run check` currently reaches `format:check` and fails on repo-wide formatter drift in untouched files; verified with untouched examples including `src/codex-env.ts`, `src/command.ts`, and `test/pr-surface-stats.test.ts`.\n",
        "branch": "codex/remove-pr-egg-hatching",
